name: Walter 'Klaus' Mitty
description:
Raised as an elf-child, it was only later, in his teenage years, that Walter discovered he was “different”. It’s a little known Christmas fact that Walter is behind the whole Santa production, making sure that things run smoothly and like clockwork as Santa travels from the North Pole through your chimney to spread the Christmas spirit.


“I’m Santa’s fastest reindeer. Who am I?”
“Where does a snowman keep his money?”
“Which of Santa’s reindeer can you see from outer space?”
“Where were the McCallisters going when they left Kevin behind?”


'r' toggles auto-rotate. ‘l’ toggles mouse following

Artist: Radarboy3000
